\nshows how details of the particle shape---beyond their aspect ratio---can be\ndetermined by a precise scattering experiment. This is of high relevance in\nunderstanding smart materials which involve suspensions of anisotropic\ncolloidal particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Mar 2015 19:12:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2015 15:36:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-31"}
