antage. But from an\nadversarial perspective it is still of significance. As an application, we\nobtain robust bounds on faking the bell violation in terms of minimum\nefficiency required using post selection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Mar 2015 20:26:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2015 19:22:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-20"}
